**Aura Teller** | Townsfolk Investigative
__Basics__
Each night, the Aura Teller may check a target to determine if they are “a threat” or “not a threat”.
__Details__
The Aura Teller cannot see a player’s role, but they can check whether or not they are a threat. Lycans, and role classified as killing roles show up as a threat.
The Aura Teller’s inspection is an immediate ability. The Aura Teller is only affected by strong disguises.
